OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry, warm
OL,6,Fand bright evening with some hazy
OL,7,Fsunny periods. Cloudier along the
OL,8,Fnorth coast, the cloud extending to
OL,9,Fall areas through the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FAnother warm or very warm
OL,12,Fday with sunny spells. Most places
OL,13,Fwill remain dry however there is the
OL,14,Frisk of a few afternoon showers in the
OL,15,Fwest.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FHot
OL,18,Fon Thursday but with the risk of heavy
OL,19,Fand thundery outbreaks of rain later
OL,20,Fin the day and into Friday. Fresher by
OL,21,FSaturday but risk of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
